text: The White River springfish (Crenichthys baileyi) is a fish that lives in North America. ==Subspecies== There are subspieces of this fish: *White River springfish (Crenichthys baileyi baileyi) *Hiko White River springfish (Crenichthys baileyi grandis) *Moapas White River springfish (Crenichthys baileyi moapae) *Preston White River springfish (Crenichthys baileyi albivallis) ==References== Category:Cyprinodontiformes Category:Animals of North America
title: Crenichthys baileyi
